<section class="benefits section" id="reasons">
	<div class="benefits__content section__content i-content">
		<header class="section__header">
			<h2 class="benefits__title section__header__title title">
													<span class="title__part benefits__title__company">Harbour.Space core values</span>

							1							<span class="benefits__item__count__dot">.</span>
						</span>
					<div class="benefits__item__content">
						<i class="benefits__item__icon"><img src="/sites/default/files/benefits/pioneering_0.svg" alt="" /></i>
						<strong class="benefits__item__title">UNIVERSITY:
REINVENTED</strong>
						<span class="benefits__item__summary">Most of academia teaches the past, we’re busy building the future. Harbour.Space is made by entrepreneurs, for entrepreneurs. We are design- led, web 3.0, omni-platform and globally interconnected. We are the makers and pioneers in our fields. We don’t care about titles and we don’t do red tape: we hire teachers based on experience and expertise, just like in the real world. We are the most relevant university of our age.</span>
						<span class="benefits__item__text"></span>
					</div>
				</li>
							<li class="benefits__item">
						<span class="benefits__item__count">
							2							<span class="benefits__item__count__dot">.</span>
						</span>
					<div class="benefits__item__content">
						<i class="benefits__item__icon"><img src="/sites/default/files/benefits/pioneers_0.svg" alt="" /></i>
						<strong class="benefits__item__title">STUDENTS ARE 
SUPER STARS</strong>
						<span class="benefits__item__summary">Harbour.Space exists for one purpose only: to help young individuals pursue knowledge, so they can progress into fulfilling and meaningful professional futures. We offer the fundamental knowledge, skills and guidance that give students the chance to make anything happen. Our students are not cogs in a machine. We celebrate our human approach by cultivating team work, interdiscipinarity, empathy and curiosity.</span>
						<span class="benefits__item__text"></span>
					</div>
				</li>
							<li class="benefits__item">
						<span class="benefits__item__count">
							3							<span class="benefits__item__count__dot">.</span>
						</span>
					<div class="benefits__item__content">
						<i class="benefits__item__icon"><img src="/sites/default/files/benefits/we marry_0.svg" alt="" /></i>
						<strong class="benefits__item__title">TECH <i class="benefits__item__title__icon benefits__item__title__icon_heart"></i> DESIGN</strong>
						<span class="benefits__item__summary">Great ideas and their realisation never come from specialists: they come from all-round visionaries. But presently, technology and design are in an arranged marriage: they are together because it’s what’s expected. We are cultivating a love marriage between the two, and we are the only university in Europe to do so. We’re doing this because the two naturally depend on one another, but experience a great lack of understanding. Interdisciplinarity is our love potion – expect sparks.</span>
						<span class="benefits__item__text"></span>
					</div>
				</li>
							<li class="benefits__item">
						<span class="benefits__item__count">
							4							<span class="benefits__item__count__dot">.</span>
						</span>
					<div class="benefits__item__content">
						<i class="benefits__item__icon"><img src="/sites/default/files/benefits/time money_0.svg" alt="" /></i>
						<strong class="benefits__item__title">TIME  MONEY</strong>
						<span class="benefits__item__summary">Youth is not for sale. That’s why we teach highly relevant and real-world responsive courses that give students a head-start even before graduation. Our programme leaders continuously scrutinise the curriculum to ensure students focus on realtime useful subjects. We teach 3-week intensive courses throughout the year, offering more learning in less time, on flexible and adaptable schedules.</span>
						<span class="benefits__item__text"></span>
					</div>
				</li>
							<li class="benefits__item">
						<span class="benefits__item__count">
							5							<span class="benefits__item__count__dot">.</span>
						</span>
					<div class="benefits__item__content">
						<i class="benefits__item__icon"><img src="/sites/default/files/benefits/compromises_0.svg" alt="" /></i>
						<strong class="benefits__item__title">NO COMPROMISES</strong>
						<span class="benefits__item__summary">If you get a place at Harbour.Space that means you get the best education. The programmes are tough and our students must work hard. We don’t sell quick-fix coding or data science courses, because they don’t exist. Only with very solid foundational knowledge of universal core concepts in science can students grow to move forward indefinitely, no matter how much the world around us changes.</span>
						<span class="benefits__item__text"></span>
					</div>
				</li>
					</ul>
	</div>

Na Terapia.   </h2>

                'ctrl+' + keyNumber

                _fn();
                return false;

                  media="screen"
                  href="//s.glbimg.com/gl/ba/css/barra-globocom.min.css"
                  type="text/css"/><script type="text/javascript">(function(){glb.barra={exibeAssineJa:true,exibeCentral:true,iframe:false};var s=document.createElement("script");s.type="text/javascript";s.async=true;s.charset="utf-8";s.src="//s.glbimg.com/gl/ba/js/barra-globocom.min.js";var ss=document.getElementsByTagName("script")[0];ss.parentNode.insertBefore(s,ss);})();</script><script type="text/javascript">
(function() {
    'use strict';

    var timerId ; // Current timer handler
    var refreshTime = 300000; // 1000*60*5
    var graceTimerStep = 10000; // 1000*10

    var isMobile = function() {
        return ($('#regua-navegacao:visible').length > 0);
    };

    var preparePlayer = function(player) {

        var refreshPageWithTimeout = function() {

            console.log('Trying to refresh on' + graceTimerStep + ' ms.');
            setTimeout(function() {
                    if (!player.isPlaying()) {
                        refreshPage();
                    }
                    console.log('Watching a video. Refresh the page later');
                }, graceTimerStep);
        };

        var playerComplete = player.complete;
        if ($.isFunction(playerComplete)) {
            player.complete = function() {
                playerComplete.apply(this, arguments);
                refreshPage();
            };
        }
        else {
            player.complete = refreshPage;
        }

        var playerOnPause = player.onPause;
        if ($.isFunction(playerOnPause)) {
            player.onPause = function() {
                playerOnPause.apply(this, arguments);
                refreshPageWithTimeout(player);
            };
        }
        else {
            player.onPause = refreshPageWithTimeout;
        }

        var playerOnStop = player.onStop;
        if ($.isFunction(playerOnStop)) {
            player.onStop = function() {
              playerOnStop.apply(this, arguments);
              refreshPageWithTimeout();
          };
        }
        else {
            player.onStop = refreshPageWithTimeout;
        }
    };

    var refreshPage = function() {
        if (!isMobile()) {
            console.log('Refreshing now');
            window.location.reload();
        }
        else {
            console.log('Is mobile: Not reloading the page.');
        }
    };

    var checkForVideoPlaying = function() {

        console.log('Timeout: Refreshing the page at any moment.');

        clearTimeout(timerId); // clear timer

        var isVideoPlaying = false;

        $.each(WM.PlayerManager, function(index, player) {
            isVideoPlaying = isVideoPlaying || player.isPlaying();
            if (player.isPlaying()) {
                preparePlayer(player);
            }
        });

        if (!isVideoPlaying) {
            refreshPage();
        }

    };

    var startTimer = function() {
        timerId = setTimeout(checkForVideoPlaying, refreshTime);
    };

    $(document).ready(function() {
        if (!isMobile() && window.location.hash != '#debug' ) {
            console.log('Time Started: ' + refreshTime + ' ms until Refresh.');
            startTimer();
        }
    });

})();
</script></body><!-- Página gerada em 26/03/2017 10:42:16 --></html>
